comment:
It amazes me when supporters of AH say 'I always believe the Victim', or 'Always believe woman' yet turn a blind eye and deaf ear to Kate James. A Woman, a Victim. Not just a victim of AH but from the original attack she endured that AH stole for her own selfish attention seeking lies.

On that Note, how can you "always believe the victim" when you don't even know who the victim is? I think you mean you "Always believe the Accuser", completely different. Anyone can make an accusation, I could say AH stole my Car. Its not true but how would you know? You'd have to believe me, after all I'm the victim.

But then AH supporters are not that bright. After all they are unable to even see why the lie about the donations is important. Donations she even claimed on TV that she HAD donated, the entire amount, not that she pledged it over a 10 year period. Its proof she lies. Lying for 4 or so years about helping Dying children and real survivors of DV. It is important showing how much she lies given that her whole 'case' revolves around her word. Her word that is disputed by moving dates, lack of injuries, no medical records, no scars, police testimony, Witnesses, impossible feats (kicking the plane chair), pointless and often incorrect details (Smeg Fridge), prior arrest of DV, Audio tapes - But sure, she only lies about everything but lets just believe her accusations that have no proof and that a judge dropped with prejudice.

Then you have the people who will finally admit that AH may have been abusive. But because they can't fathom a woman being an aggressor, a woman being in the wrong with no fault on the man. They spout 'Mutual abuse', and that 'Depp is not perfect', when there is literally not proof he did anything other than an accidental headbutt that would count as Self defence. Texts messages where he rants about his abuser to a friend than says he could never hurt her. Hitting cupboards due to money he lost while the accuser secretly films and smirks into the camera.

Also yes, Depp has had Drinking and drug issues but that does not make him abusive. One woman making claims without proof does not make it fact. All her simps out there acting like AH doesn't have a drug and alcohol problem herself. That she wasn't previously arrested for DV. That she used dying children and DV survivors for attention. You're blind and ignorant and don't want to see what is right in front of your eyes. 

Amber Heard is a domestic abuser. She is an insult to true victims and survivors. She is an insult to woman.
She does not get a free pass for being a woman. She does not get a free pass for being Bisexual. She does not get a free pass because she's 'famous' or 'pretty'.
She has abused multiple people. She is a proven racist and is disrespectful of religion. She Used dying children and she used DV survivors. She joked and made fun of another countries laws in which she broke.. and on top of all that, she is an actress that can't even act. Completely replaceable with a plank of wood.

All Johnny Depp did wrong was fall in love, with a pathological lying gold-digger.
